# Research

A tech tree of 8 unlockable nodes that provide passive bonuses to the zoo. Research requires spending money and waiting for progress to complete. Nodes have prerequisites forming a directed graph. The research system provides mid-to-late-game goals that reward sustained play.

## Tech Tree Graph

```
                    Efficient Feeding ($2,000)
                           |
                    Breeding Program ($3,000)
                      /           \
      Advanced Enclosures       Exotic Species
           ($4,500)                ($6,750)
               |
        Veterinary Care
           ($6,750)

                    Marketing ($2,000)
                      /           \
              Gift Shop           Night Zoo
              ($4,500)            ($4,500)
```

